Package: BrainTemplates
Type: Package
Title:  Some commonly used brain atlases, including AAL and HarvardOxford
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2016-03-11
Author: Haixiao Du
Maintainer: Haixiao Du <duhx11@tsinghua.edu.cn>
Description: Provides the some widely-used brain parcelation atlases 
		for the neuroimaging data analysis for both ROI-based and 
		voxel-based studies. Atlases are stored as objects of NIdata 
		class, and should be resliced to match the resolution and dimensions
		of specific dataset used. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.2)
Suggests: Brainbase
NeedsCompilation: no

